title: Brunei Consumer Price Index Cpi
description: Consumer Price Index CPI in Brunei increased to 107.20 points in August from 106.60 points in July of 2022. Consumer Price Index CPI in Brunei averaged 100.57 points from 2015 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 107.20 points in August of 2022 and a record low of 98.40 points in June of 2019. This page provides - Brunei Consumer Price Index Cpi- actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: Department of Economic Planning and Development, Brunei
